      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Flatside Wilderness Additions Act</strong></p> <p>This bill adds specified lands to the Flatside Wilderness in the Ouachita National Forest in Arkansas. The bill also redesignates the wilderness as the Flatside-Bethune Wilderness.</p>",
